title: How to Recreate the Growls and Synths in Skrillex - First of the Year [FL Studio/Massive Tutorial]
description: This is my tutorial on how to recreate some of the growls and synths in Skrillex's "First of the Year (Equinox)." I use FL Studio, Massive and the WOW filter for most of it. BUY FL Studio: http://affiliate.image-line.com/GHBDE... BUY Massive: http://www.native-instruments.com/en/... BUY WOW Filter: http://www.sugar-bytes.de/content/pro... I realize that Skrillex uses FM8 for most of these growls but I unfortunately cannot afford that at the moment. Subscribe for more!
